cast.overview: When Pete and Ellie decide to start a family, they stumble into the world of foster care adoption. They hope to take in one small child but when they meet three siblings, including a rebellious 15 year old girl, they find themselves speeding from zero to three kids overnight.
cast.title: Instant Family

details.biography: Allyn Rachel is an American actor, comedian, and writer best known from a variety of national commercials that began airing in the United States in 2011. She co-created the web series Couple Time with her boyfriend Patrick Carlyle, which is now in development at FOX.
details.name: Allyn Rachel
